<h1>The following makes use of the abbr function to abbreviate</h1>
<p>I used to compete in <abbr title="World Taekwondo Federation">WTF</abbr> </p>


<h1>The following is an example of block quotes</h1>
<blockquote>
    <p>A line will be placed to the left of this text.</p>
    <footer>This is the place for references</footer>
  </blockquote>

<h1>The following is an example of a right block quote</h1>
<blockquote class="blockquote-reverse">
<p>For 50 years, WWF has been protecting the future of nature. The world's leading conservation organization, WWF works in 100 countries and is supported by 1.2 million members in the United States and close to 5 million globally.</p>
    <footer>This reference appears on the right side</footer>
  </blockquote>

